OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy on Monday with a few showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain spreading south.
OL,8,FMainly dry and bright on Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday, but the east coast
OL,10,Fgenerally cloudier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
